{"tid":782536,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【犯罪家族】黃桂芬「自殺案」 5大謎團","createTime":"2018-08-16T22:31:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T12:36:22.000Z","uid":29269,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"215c74fdbba4544f4a598770f5fabc0af2ed6123","tid":782536,"uid":29269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T22:31:28.000Z","msg":"【犯罪家族】黃桂芬「自殺案」 5大謎團<br />\n黃桂芬前天獲准保釋後5個多小時，被發現從油麻地多層停車場8樓墮下斃命，其二弟黃桂榮13小時後自首。警方在黃桂芬墮斃現場發現4封遺書，調查後以匿名向傳媒放風稱，黃桂芬患有情緒病，「相信死因無可疑」，料稍後遞交死亡報告予死因裁判官。這宗離奇案件留下多個疑團未解。<br />\n1.若黃桂芬如警方放風稱身患情緒病，何以仍有足夠精神狀態，策劃以放數為名、禁錮勒索為實的跨境罪行？<br />\n2.曾犯下無數重案入獄11年，區區一單詐騙案對惡貫滿盈的黃桂芬實在微不足道，畏罪尋死之說講得通嗎？<br />\n3.被捕後花數以十萬元計聘請星級大狀上庭付100萬元保釋金，為何5小時後即自尋短見？<br />\n4.撰寫遺書，更一度寫4封，是否符合黃桂芬的風格？<br />\n5.黃桂芬墮斃13小時後，為何一直成功逃過警方耳目的胞弟黃桂榮便自首投案？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/063048_0e9f2a7c2e71d1e7addbb1ff7da701fc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F063048_0e9f2a7c2e71d1e7addbb1ff7da701fc.png&h=be42b465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180816/58572884\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180816%2F58572884&d=A7mLzLvfcAnHC%2Bsm7SmLdwIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=2714ac7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180816%2F58572884&h=9b895df0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180816/58572884</a>"},{"pid":"3c19b5c37ce1556d1fd57982b283f9a91ef0bc19","tid":782536,"uid":130879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T00:30:56.000Z","msg":"又想搵人做義工破案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7dbf57936227d929a654d8874f502eecb2211ba","tid":782536,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201